==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Angle of entry
<hw>An"gle of en"try</hw>. <fld>(A⟦eum⟧ronautics)</fld> <def>The angle
between the tangent to the advancing edge (of an a⟦eum⟧rocurve) and the
line of motion; -- contrasted with <contr>angle of trail</contr>, which
is the angle between the tangent to the following edge and the line of
motion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Angle of incidence</ent>⟦br⟧
